  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LoginException

    public class PermissionException
extends SOAPSenderException
    Thrown when the authenticated SOAP user does not have permission to perform the requested operation. This is also may be thrown by the rest framework as well when the rest user does not have the required permissions.
